            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>mayo </strong>and <strong>cider vinegar</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>creamy dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
