      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash, then cut your<strong> lettuce</strong> into quarters, lengthways and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Use the remaining time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
