    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything's done, remove the<strong> BBQ hoisin chicken thigh</strong> from the oven</p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the<strong> sliced brioche</strong> to a baking tray, cut-side down and put the tray in the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
