        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>cooked chicken thigh</strong> from the dish to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks – this technique is known as pulling</p><p>Return the <strong>pulled chicken thigh </strong>to the dish and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> pulled BBQ hoisin chicken thigh</strong></p>",
