    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, fill the <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>brioche bun</strong> with the <strong>pulled BBQ hoisin chicken thigh</strong> and a drizzle of the <strong>creamy dressing </strong>(save the rest for the salad!) – this is your <strong>pulled BBQ hoisin chicken thigh burger</strong> </p><p>Serve with the<strong> lettuce wedges</strong> and <strong>chips</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the<strong> remaining creamy dressing</strong> over the<strong> </strong>lettuce</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
